<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>A Message From Me</title>

  <!-- Google Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500&family=Inter:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 12px 26px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      background: transparent;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e5e7eb;
      color: #0f172a;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .hidden {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      line-height: 1.9;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 35px;
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0.7;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 25px 18px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>I Owe You an Apology</h1>

    <p>
      I’ve taken time to reflect, and I want to say this honestly — I was wrong.<br><br>

      I didn’t handle things the way I should have, and I understand that my actions hurt you.
      There’s no justification for that, and I take full responsibility.<br><br>

      I’m not writing this to change your mind or ask for anything.
      I just believe you deserved a sincere and respectful apology.<br><br>

      What we had meant something to me, and I regret not valuing it the way I should have when it mattered.
    </p>

    <button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Read More</button>

    <div id="message" class="hidden">
      I’m working on myself — quietly and consistently.<br><br>

      Not to prove anything, but because I understand where I went wrong.<br><br>

      Whether or not we ever speak again, I genuinely wish you peace, happiness, and everything good in life.<br><br>

      I’m truly sorry.
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
      — From someone who learned the hard way
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function showMessage() {
      document.getElementById("message").style.display = "block";
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
